Creates a new EncryptedSystemWebViewClient.

Parameters:
systemWebViewEngine - the SystemWebViewEngine to delegate to.
assetManager - the AssetManager that is used create InputStream's for assets.
encryptedAssetPrefix - a magic prefix value by which the assets to be decrypted can be recognized.
assetInputStreamFactory - the input stream factory that can decrypt the assets.
